        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "desc",
          "source": "How resolved comments appear in the editor.",
          "target": "已解决评论在编辑器中的显示方式。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "desc",
          "source": "Where the add-comment form appears. The side panel keeps the document visible while you draft.",
          "target": "添加评论表单出现的位置。侧边面板可在您撰写时保持文档可见。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "desc",
          "source": "Comments are invisible in reading view (markers are HTML comments). Show a note-level banner with totals, a badge on each section that has comments, or both. Click an indicator to open the comment panel. Counts are threads; replies are not counted.",
          "target": "在阅读视图中评论不可见（标记为HTML注释）。显示包含总数的笔记级横幅、每个有评论的章节上的徽章，或两者都显示。点击指示器可打开评论面板。计数为讨论串；回复不计入。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "desc",
          "source": "When the thread panel shows comments from multiple files, collapse files other than the one you are editing. Click a file header to expand it manually.",
          "target": "当讨论串面板显示来自多个文件的评论时，折叠除您正在编辑的文件以外的其他文件。点击文件标题可手动展开。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "desc",
